Crazy that we're already three months into 2022! In Q1, the NFT.Storage team brought you [delegated uploads using UCANs](UCANDocs), a [faster HTTP IPFS gateway for NFTs](https://nft.storage/docs/concepts/gateways/), and more. We also crossed 50M uploads as a service! But the momentum doesn't stop there - continue reading to learn about what's in store for Q2.

